   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Burundi Climate Change Resilience Support project</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">In Burundi, climate change has significantly affected the lives of people and other natural beings. Increased waste, greenhouse gas emissions levels, deforestation and flood-induced disasters threaten irreversible consequences for our planet&apos;s climate systems and challenge the resilience of Burundian communities in the face of climate change.  This project aims to create agro-forest nurseries, manage waste through recycling and promote environmental justice.</narrative>
  </description>
